#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:1 of
msgid "Read text from clipboard and pass to :func:`~pandas.read_csv`."
msgstr "从剪贴板读取文本并传递给 :func:`~pandas.read_csv`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:3 of
msgid ""
"Parses clipboard contents similar to how CSV files are parsed using "
":func:`~pandas.read_csv`."
msgstr "解析剪贴板内容的方式类似于使用 :func:`~pandas.read_csv` 解析 CSV 文件。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:6 of
msgid ""
"A string or regex delimiter. The default of ``'\\s+'`` denotes one or "
"more whitespace characters."
msgstr "字符串或正则表达式分隔符。默认值 ``'\\s+'`` 表示一个或多个空白字符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:9 of
msgid "See :func:`~pandas.read_csv` for the full argument list."
msgstr "完整参数列表请参见 :func:`~pandas.read_csv`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:11 of
msgid "A parsed :class:`DataFrame` object."
msgstr "解析后的 :class:`DataFrame` 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:16 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.to_clipboard`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:17 of
msgid "Copy object to the system clipboard."
msgstr "将对象复制到系统剪贴板。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`read_csv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:20 of
msgid "Read a comma-separated values (csv) file into DataFrame."
msgstr "将逗号分隔值 (csv) 文件读入 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`read_fwf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.direct.read_clipboard:23 of
msgid "Read a table of fixed-width formatted lines into DataFrame."
msgstr "将固定宽度格式的行表格读入 DataFrame。"

